# Keep the build context small and never ship local/dev artefacts or secrets.
**/node_modules
.git
.gitea
.forgejo
**/dist
**/.nuxt
**/.output
**/.nitro
**/.cache
**/.pnpm-store
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
.vscode
.idea
# Secrets — only .env.example may ship, real envs are injected at runtime.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
